data.title: rn723 All
data.meta_description: rn723-all - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document provides an overview of upcoming releases from Delmark Records, a jazz and blues record label. It announces reissues of classic albums by Magic Sam, Junior Wells, and Clarence "Jelly" Johnson. It also previews new albums from Grana' Louise, Ernest Dawkins and his New Horizons Ensemble, and Mississippi Heat. It discusses awards won by Mississippi Heat and their producer Michael Freeman and studio sessions with Pinetop Perkins and Quintus McCormick.
